-- Returns:
--
-- a **sequence** containing two elements:
--# an **integer** status code, whose values can be:
--* //1//: New file.
--* //0//: Normal, existing file.
--* //-1//: Operation cancelled.
--# a **string**: containing the full pathname of the selected file
--
